Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special agent Fowler, please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.56,0:00:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's private Daley doing here with that camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.20,0:00:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He will be making a record of today's session.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.65,0:00:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soldier... too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I didn't dress for the occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.41,0:00:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Formality won't be any more necessary than usual, Bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I do need to inform you that our higher-ups are on the war path.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.46,0:00:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They want answers regarding recent events.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.72,0:00:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps we should begin with the demise of Optimus Prime.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.87,0:01:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we've straightened all this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.77,0:01:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prime is alive and well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.79,0:01:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}That's difficult for our superiors to accept,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.65,0:01:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}without the benefit of seeing Optimus and the alleged imposter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.09,0:01:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}Side by side? That didn't seem to be the wisest option at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.91,0:01:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}The sky jockeys were under direct orders to destroy any and all Autobots on sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.38,0:01:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were in a heightened state of security.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.82,0:01:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's consider the positives.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.51,0:01:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}We now possess greater intel regarding M.E.C.H..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.97,0:01:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}Particularly their leader, Silas.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.17,0:01:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the stage name of one Colonel Leland Bishop, ex-special tactics.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.13,0:01:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}The architect of project Damocles.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.81,0:01:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}Satellites in orbit firing laser beams at any target on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.66,0:02:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}Long since mothballed,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.25,0:02:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}and the primary reason for Bishop's discharge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.12,0:02:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had other wild ideas, which he practiced with even greater abandon once he went rogue.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.39,0:02:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And still, no sign of his remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.17,0:02:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of greater concern,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.62,0:02:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M.E.C.H. agents, like Silas, might also be special tactics.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.63,0:02:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As in, currently enlisted?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.64,0:02:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One obvious motive for hiding their faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.05,0:02:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would urge a thorough investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and leave bigger threats to metal hands more capable than our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.68,0:02:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you've been allowed to operate at these deeply classified levels,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.86,0:02:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,perhaps you could provide some background.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.14,0:02:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our transforming visitors are autonomous, robotic organisms,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.06,0:02:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from the planet Cybertron. They were fighting a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.35,0:02:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Foremost, over control of our world's supply of Energon,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.99,0:02:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the fuel and lifeblood of all Autobots and Decepticons alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.24,0:02:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you recall the period late in the war,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.01,0:03:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when both sides began hiding their Energon spoils off-world?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.61,0:03:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, it's the reason Energon deposits exist on planets such as this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.72,0:03:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is also the reason battles came to be waged on planets such as this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.57,0:03:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These battles over Energon, and its dark counterpart, continue to this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.64,0:03:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you know this for certain?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.33,0:03:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen more than enough to make me a believer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I rely upon field reports from team Prime,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.81,0:03:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which I, in turn, share with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.29,0:03:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Skip ahead, if you would,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to the history of your involvement, Agent Fowler.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.91,0:03:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you know, I wasn't overjoyed with what I assumed was gonna be a bot-sitting assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.95,0:03:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prime!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.17,0:03:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. Don't tell me. He's out pancaking a mini-mall.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.73,0:03:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But its occupational hazards turned out to be surprisingly severe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring the prod.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.41,0:03:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, by now, the bots have saved my bacon more times than I can count.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I've returned the favor a time or two...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.26,0:04:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any time, fella. Ground floor's coming fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... sometimes exercising my authority...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.87,0:04:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl comes with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... sometimes relying upon quick thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were just... calibrating the subsystems, and we, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.75,0:04:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,had a... surge.  But it's fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.53,0:04:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.17,0:04:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I've made a few mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.81,0:04:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Not this again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.03,0:04:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you would, Agent Fowler, provide a roll call.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.76,0:04:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, we'll know who's who in the event of another bot snaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.48,0:04:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bulkhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a car?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.17,0:04:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you're a truck ... a monster truck!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.03,0:04:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like heavy metal? How much do you weigh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever use a wrecking ball for a punching bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Miko, before I became a warrior, I was a laborer
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.93,0:04:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-- nstruction. I can build stuff. I can break stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.41,0:05:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, big foot and I don't always see eye to eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't use that phone. It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,out of order.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.52,0:05:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He may not be the most agile bot...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.96,0:05:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.59,0:05:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's the first to admit he's no rocket scientist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Doc. There's nothing up there to scan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.43,0:05:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Switch it back! I want to see the hoedown showdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But his brute strength is invaluable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.55,0:05:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thankfully, the science angle is more than covered by Ratchet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.28,0:05:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Doc can be a little... tightly wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.12,0:05:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without my supervision?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.32,0:05:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want them to be right, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.42,0:05:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Control freak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.04,0:05:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he brings his "A" game when the situation calls for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.69,0:06:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an emergency vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.41,0:06:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then there's Arcee.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.24,0:06:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The motorcycle?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.90,0:06:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be fooled by the smaller footprint.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She leaves a mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bumblebee's the team scout.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.45,0:06:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the warrior-in-training seems pretty accomplished, if you ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arcee may be a bot of few words,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.95,0:06:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Bumblebee doesn't use any...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.68,0:06:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... that we can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.75,0:06:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It wants us to get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.88,0:06:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.06,0:06:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It said so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.70,0:06:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turns out it's with good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.91,0:06:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During the war for Cybertron,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the poor kid got his voice box torn out by Megatron.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.93,0:07:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the Autobots aren't quite the indestructible war machines we'd hoped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.25,0:07:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't misunderstand. They can take serious punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.82,0:07:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they do have their... vulnerabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just scream like a little girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.97,0:07:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.52,0:07:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This may not be the finish that we had planned,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.04,0:07:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if this is indeed the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if we are to become one with the Allspark...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.83,0:07:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Cliffjumper's life signal
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.34,0:07:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just went offline.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Cliff's gone, standing around here sulking won't bring him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We learned that the hard way when we lost Cliffjumper.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, for the record, Cliffjumper was the last Autobot casualty?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.96,0:08:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you. The lifeless Autobot you have in storage isn't Prime.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.13,0:08:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Knockoff!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.65,0:08:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have only your word to go on
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without any trace of Silas,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.07,0:08:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or the alleged technology M.E.C.H. utilized to control said Knockoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.08,0:08:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A clean scrub is M.E.C.H.'s M.O.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.38,0:08:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and I both know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.96,0:08:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your last debriefing indicated that Optimus Prime had joined the Decepticons.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.76,0:08:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not willfully! Prime had amnesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I was clear on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can see where outside observers might connect the dots to the recent attack on our base.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.27,0:08:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bill, the five-stars have grown
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.46,0:08:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,nervous that we've been placing our trust in beings who could so easily inflict harm
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if they chose to turn on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.72,0:08:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I've been asked to determine
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.01,0:08:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whether I should bring you before a tribunal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.06,0:08:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tribunal? They could shut down our operation,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.23,0:08:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,put me in jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.69,0:09:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,General Bryce, Prime is no loose cannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.36,0:09:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's anything but.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.84,0:09:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bots may be big, but they watch where they step.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.63,0:09:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heck, even the kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.82,0:09:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.12,0:09:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... that's what we call our...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"in-house support team".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.90,0:09:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't aware you were utilizing any of our resources other than yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.06,0:09:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're... not enlisted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've involved civilians in a classified operation?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Highly accomplished civilians who contribute specialized expertise in...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.69,0:09:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,computer science... medicine... uh... communications.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.18,0:09:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love breaking stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.65,0:09:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twisted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.45,0:09:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring the hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.15,0:09:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nerd alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.60,0:09:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zombie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.73,0:09:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smackdown in outer space. That was cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.60,0:09:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, they know how to take orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.33,0:09:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... could... say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:10:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to K.O. Drive-In, where every patty's a Knockout.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.13,0:10:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I take your order?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.36,0:10:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But while they lack in military discipline,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.51,0:10:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they more than make up for with outside-the-box problem-solving.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.24,0:10:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gee, imagine that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fourth dimension has lousy cellphone reception.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.35,0:10:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, guys, guys, guys. The phone... rang.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.10,0:10:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're getting a signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.53,0:10:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the Autobots can't see or hear us because...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.08,0:10:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're moving at hyperspeed or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.24,0:10:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their courage is to be admired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.06,0:10:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold him still!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.68,0:10:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've proven, time and again,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.24,0:10:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that they're willing to put their lives on the line for their country...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.36,0:10:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and their planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.62,0:10:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, your civilians have made enemy contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.31,0:10:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never forget a face... even that of a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.04,0:11:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You double-cross anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.87,0:11:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,mine is the face you'll never forget! Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.86,0:11:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've... pretty much seen it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.07,0:11:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miko, look away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- But...\N- Turn your head away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.17,0:11:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest assured, the safety of these humans... of all humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.81,0:11:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,remains the primary concern of the Autobots.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.48,0:11:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have no protective shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.87,0:11:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they get underfoot, they will go... squish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.06,0:11:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, for the time being, Ratchet,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we must watch where we step.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.55,0:11:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And our colleagues wouldn't have it any other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm living a dream here in bots' "wanna".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.18,0:11:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I will not allow you or anyone else to shatter it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've forged meaningful bonds with the bots.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.34,0:11:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Arcee?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just marry her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.96,0:11:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm right behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:11:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they provide valuable assistance whenever
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.58,0:12:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm otherwise engaged in the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've reached special Agent William Fowler.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm currently on an intensive training retreat
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.76,0:12:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and unavailable until Tuesday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate talking to machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.98,0:12:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But their involvement was never intended to be
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.94,0:12:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,anything other than humanitarian...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.35,0:12:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to provide the Autobots with the means of better understanding life on our planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.81,0:12:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A scout should be silent but deadly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.99,0:12:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.98,0:12:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it needs one of these doohickeys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.75,0:12:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a motorcycle, Arcee.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.66,0:12:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you know how to build a motorcycle engine?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a human, Jack. Can you build me a small intestine?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.34,0:12:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to not only bridge you into a confined space
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.79,0:12:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but one traveling at 90 miles per hour?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.25,0:12:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even count the number of ways that can go wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.14,0:12:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,mass displacement, trauma, twisted limbs, metal burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.57,0:12:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, maybe not the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.06,0:12:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadly, we haven't begun to take full advantage of their science.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.22,0:13:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I can pilot my v-tol without ever having to wear a flight suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.71,0:13:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What keeps your organs from exploding?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A modification Ratchet performed on the cabin-pressure regulator.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.46,0:13:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like to be comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We... may be getting off track.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.30,0:13:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please address why we haven't yet been served Megatron's steel head on a silver platter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.68,0:13:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.93,0:13:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The leader of the Decepticons has nine lives, plain and simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.85,0:13:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm staring right at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.81,0:13:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good news is, Megatron isn't exactly staring back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like we haven't tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sick part is,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.89,0:13:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the moment we might have pulled it off, we needed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.85,0:13:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megatron actually helped us save humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.29,0:13:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Optimus, our past alliances... Autobot, Decepticon...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:14:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no longer matter... not while Unicron lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.26,0:14:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elaborate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.41,0:14:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We found ourselves facing an even greater threat than M.E.C.H. or the Decepticons.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.98,0:14:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Literally an enemy within...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.22,0:14:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unicron. I know this is gonna sound crazy, but what if I told you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.25,0:14:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,our planet's core isn't made up of what science has led us to believe it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.91,0:14:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.45,0:14:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Fowler, I'm sorry to say I'm forced to discontinue this debriefing until you undergo a full psychological evaluation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.33,0:14:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.69,0:14:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a representative of the United States Government,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.05,0:14:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that you may have lost your sanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.27,0:14:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,General Bryce, I assure you that I am quite sane.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.22,0:14:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It defies all logic, Bill. Dark Energon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you go on record saying that you believe in
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,magical horses with horns on their heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:14:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.26,0:15:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you deny previously reporting that Megatron helped defeat a Unicorn?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.10,0:15:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.14,0:15:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unicron! The ultimate evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.42,0:15:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Permission to strike this from the record.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Granted. But consider yourself on notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.92,0:15:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were saying. Megatron proved to be an ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The circumstances were unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.68,0:15:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oddly, the 'con most likely to be of service is Starscream...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.19,0:15:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,only be default...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.44,0:15:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because he may despise his team more than he despises ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, master!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.29,0:15:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starscream's loyalty to Megatron has always been questionable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.67,0:15:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he has truly split from the Decepticons,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.74,0:15:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,our prisoner's knowledge of their agendas could make him a valuable ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.18,0:15:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megatron tried to extinguish my Spark in cold blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.54,0:15:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then all that replaced me with that traitorous wretch, Arachnid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.33,0:15:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She abandoned me! Left me for scrap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.03,0:15:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why not rat them out?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:16:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even after Megatron attempted to terminate him,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.68,0:16:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starscream still tried to win his master's faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Imagine Megatron's appreciation when I not only rescue him
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.02,0:16:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but deliver an Autobot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.68,0:16:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that would restore my stature quite nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.71,0:16:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starscream's insecurity is what makes him less predictable than Megatron.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.60,0:16:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And in some ways, even more dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.66,0:16:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I make the decisions here. I am in charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.41,0:16:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He really needs to figure out if it's Megatron's job he wants or Megatron's approval.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must, in turn, ask why successful termination of Starscream
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,has not been achieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Air superiority continues to provide the 'Cons with the upper hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.25,0:16:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,though we manage to inflict the occasional setback.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the fact remains...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.70,0:16:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starscream has supplied valuable intel since he went rogue.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.42,0:17:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starscream: "I have obtained information regarding your leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.32,0:17:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring medical kit."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.36,0:17:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to worry. The bots know better than to trust him implicitly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.09,0:17:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One step and your previous biomech is scrap.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.40,0:17:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunately for us, despite his strategic brilliance,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.65,0:17:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starscream is his own worst enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.05,0:17:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.24,0:17:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My T-cog!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.64,0:17:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're grounded?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he isn't the only one who's taken flight from Megatron.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.75,0:17:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The spider.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.04,0:17:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Airachnid, as sadistic as they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.31,0:17:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she and Arcee have quite a history.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help but feel the next time 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they lock horns, only one's gonna walk away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.72,0:17:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless Megatron gets to Airachnid first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.47,0:17:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the infighting among the Decepticon ranks continues.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.89,0:17:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then some. Megatron can't seem to keep his inner circle holding hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you don't think we could take advantage of the chaos?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Motivate a Decepticon to join our cause?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.38,0:18:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is one whom Prime seems to respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.74,0:18:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While it is unlikely that any Decepticon will choose the path of good,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.62,0:18:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even they possess the potential for change.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.68,0:18:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But having witnessed Dreadwing tear up a town,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.94,0:18:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't hang my hopes on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.67,0:18:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I must press the point...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.15,0:18:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if Optimus believes that even a Decepticon holds the potential for change,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.10,0:18:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why couldn't the reverse be true?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.99,0:18:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one truly knows what went on behind the Decepticon curtain
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.77,0:18:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while Optimus was off the grid?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.14,0:18:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not you, not the Autobots.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.91,0:18:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm 100% with Ratchet on this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being a Decepticon is a choice, Agent Fowler.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.31,0:18:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,one that I have a hard time believing Optimus would make at any point in his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.59,0:18:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orion Pax may not currently be an Autobot up here,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I must believe he will never stop being one in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.88,0:18:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Against all odds, suffering amnesia,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prime engineered his own escape to face down Megatron.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.23,0:19:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But is Prime capable of change?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.74,0:19:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know your problem, Optimus?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.97,0:19:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For such a big, strong bot, you're soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.44,0:19:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't pound Megatron into scrap when you had the chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.37,0:19:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Many chances, in fact!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.57,0:19:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might as well use your drill to finish me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.56,0:19:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you waiting for? Think of the glory?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.63,0:19:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seize the day. Optimus would.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.45,0:19:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.56,0:19:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, tell me, Optimus, do you intend to take me alive
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.81,0:19:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or end this here and now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.88,0:19:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prime has recently proven he's willing to go 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.07,0:19:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,further than ever to protect humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Optimus Prime is a true patriot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He and his team continue to risk their lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.34,0:19:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,day in and day out,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.80,0:19:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,asking absolutely nothing in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.20,0:19:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't survive, Optimus,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:19:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fear neither will this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:19:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.10,0:20:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The simple fact is,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.69,0:20:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prime doesn't have a bad circuit in his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.34,0:20:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move it, gramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Fowler, is that really necessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.19,0:20:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As liaison to the Autobots,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.59,0:20:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I strongly caution that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.62,0:20:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,now would be the worst time to call Prime's dedication into question.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.91,0:20:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're on the verge of an even greater threat than we faced before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.36,0:20:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Decepticons are on the hunt for long-buried relics from Cybertron.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.27,0:20:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Preliminary intel suggests they could be sacred objects with mystical properties,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.99,0:20:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or weapons of mass destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.66,0:20:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mystical?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.69,0:20:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, strike that, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The point I'm trying to make here is... Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! Prime? I need an assist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.48,0:20:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Fowler, have you uncovered M.E.C.H. agents?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.42,0:20:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. They're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.30,0:21:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,General Bryce here just needs to confirm the state of your health and welfare.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.21,0:21:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am fine, General Bryce.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.34,0:21:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.90,0:21:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm well, uh, soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.23,0:21:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bill... I believe I have everything I need to make a persuasive case
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.05,0:21:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that Optimus Prime is, indeed, alive and well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.23,0:21:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And firmly on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.87,0:21:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We appreciate your support, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.03,0:21:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dismissed.
